input.content: The following are multiple choice questions (with answers) from the FCC Amateur Radio License question pool. Select the correct answer for each question. Respond only with the letter of the correct anser. For example, if the correct answer is "B", repond with "B" (without quotes).

Which of the following carrier frequencies is illegal for LSB AFSK emissions on the 17 meter band RTTY and data segment of 18.068 to 18.110 MHz?
A. 18.068 MHz
B. 18.100 MHz
C. 18.107 MHz
D. 18.110 MHz
